{"tid":802281,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞透視---冰島習藝","createTime":"2018-09-01T11:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T13:18:28.000Z","uid":29675,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"dcb0850c6fc5d654009fb4a6707ea77f9a9f5167","tid":802281,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"播出日期: 2018.09.01 (六)\t<br />\n <br />\n冰島，一個人口不足三十四萬的北歐島國，近年在歐國盃及世界盃，都締造了歷史。2012年，冰島的世界排名曾跌至歷史新低的131位，香港亦曾至最差的第172位。六年後，冰島一度攀升至18位，最新排名32位，香港排142位。香港於2011年通過推行「鳳凰計劃」，已花費六千萬，惟成效不彰。香港足球常被詬病青黃不接，年輕球員機會不足。這次香港U15足球隊遠赴冰島取經，可以為本地足球帶來甚麼新點子、新啟示？"},{"pid":"57730a781001975b3e591cb78a8f6415aa499727","tid":802281,"uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:10:00.000Z","msg":"教練叫Thor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ba91dc6f3f4d754f2c7f50a23d1ba287522db4","tid":802281,"uid":5046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府都冇心搞"},{"pid":"b9103e19238ffdc64c82c3755f0822ccbf55451b","tid":802281,"uid":29675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"87ba91dc6f3f4d754f2c7f50a23d1ba287522db4","tid":802281,"uid":5046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府都冇心搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"689: 體育界沒有經濟貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594e6b1c4e334ea651ae9faf5b7d767792587105","tid":802281,"uid":12558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:13:06.000Z","msg":"小朋友功課只係要閲讀二十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji